query: SELECT id,email,last_login FROM users WHERE email = $1
SELECT * FROM orders WHERE created_at >= $1 AND created_at < $2 ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 200
UPDATE sessions SET expires_at = $1 WHERE session_token = $2
SELECT u.id, COUNT(*) FROM users u JOIN events e ON e.user_id=u.id WHERE e.type=$1 GROUP BY u.id ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 50
SELECT * FROM invoices WHERE account_id=$1 AND status=$2 ORDER BY due_date ASC
